text:
Justin Bieber and Selena Gomez Go to the Airport Ahead of Valentine's Day





Updated: About 2 days ago

Set to celebrate Valentine! Justin Bieber and Selena Gomez were caught together while heading towards the LAX airport on Saturday.

They were photographed in an SUV on the way to the airport in L.A., a few days before Valentine's Day. However, it's not been revealed that where Justin and Selena (Jelena) are going, one possibility might be New York City.

Justin Bieber and Selena Gomez Go to the Airport Ahead of Valentine's Day

Source: eonline

Selena is believed to be attending Coach's New York Fashion Week show on Tuesday, February 13. So if the couple was spotted heading to the airport, we can assume that they are both heading to NYC.

After their official reunion last year, the two lovebirds are still going strong together.

Selena and Justin have been in an on-off relationship over the years, but a source close to the couple said in January that "everything is so different this time around."

The source shared,

This time around, Justin is behaving like a gentlemen and showing how much he cares about her. He's is a lot more open about his feelings towards Selena, which has been a big sign of him maturing.

As previously reported, the duo was caught poolside at Montage hotel in Laguna Beach, California. TMZ was able to shoot video of the couple at the hotel.
